1. [...] X X [...] šu-luh kug-ga tum₂-ma
#lem: X; X; X; X; šuluh[ritual cleansing]; kug[pure]; tum[suitable]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. {[d]}ri-im-{d}suen išib an-na sizkur sikil-la tum₂-ma
#lem: Rimsin[1]RN; išib[purification priest]; An[1]DN; siškur[prayer]; sikil[pure]; tum[suitable]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. [... šag₄] kug-ta bi₂-pad₃-da-zu nam-en kalam-ma-še₃ i-ni-il₂-la
#lem: X; šag[heart]; kug[pure]; pad[find]; namen[the office of en-priest]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; il[raise]
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. nam-sipad saŋ gig₂-ga i-ni-in-ŋar-ra
#lem: namsipad[shepherdship]; saŋ[head]; giggig[black]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. ešgiri₂ kalam ge-en-ge-en šu-ni bi₂-in-si-a
#lem: ešgiri[staff]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; gin[confirm]; šu[hand]; si[fill]
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. šibir uŋ₃ zi-ŋal₂ lah₅-lah₅-e zag-ga-na bi₂-in-la₂
#lem: šibir[shepherd's staff]; uŋ[people]; ziŋal[living things]; lah[plural stem of tum ⟦bring⟧]; zag[side]; la[hang]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. ša-ra-da-gub šu sikil-la ak-a-ni niŋ₂-nam mi-ni-in-dug₃-dug₃
#lem: gub[stand]; šu[hand]; sikil[pure]; ak[do]; niŋnam[anything]; dug[good]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. ga {d}ezina₂-ma ir dug₃-ga ma-dam kalam-ma-ka
#lem: ga[milk]; Ezina[1]DN; ir[smell]; dug[good]; madam[abundance]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. he-nun šag₄-tum₂-ma he₂-ŋal₂ nu-silig-ge
#lem: henun[plenty]; šagtum[pasture land]; heŋal[plenty]; silig[cease]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. kurun ŋeštin pa e₃-a
#lem: kurun[beer]; ŋeštin[vine]; pa[branch]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. {kaš}ulušin₃ ku₇-ku₇-da a₂ sikil-da šar₂-ra
#lem: ulušin[date-sweetened emmer-beer]; kud[sweet]; a[arm]; sikil[pure]; šar[mix]
#etcsl: line-id=11

12. kaš er₉ ki sikil ŋeštin# tab-ba a naŋ nam-en-na-zu
#lem: kaš[beer]; ir[mighty]; ki[place]; sikil[purify]; ŋeštin[vine]; tab[double]; a[water]; naŋ[drink]; namen[the office of en-priest]
#etcsl: line-id=12

13. kaš tab-ba kaš mah šu kug-zu tum₂-ma
#lem: kaš[beer]; tab[double]; kaš[beer]; mah[great]; šu[hand]; kug[pure]; tum[suitable]
#etcsl: line-id=13

14. lal₃ babbar mu pad₃-da-zu hur-saŋ-ta e₃-a
#lem: lal[syrup]; babbar[white]; mu[name]; pad[find]; hursaŋ[mountain]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=14

