#lem: iŋeš[sesame oil]; barag[press?]; i[oil]; lib[high quality]; saŋ[head]; sig[put into]
#etcsl: line-id=16

17. gara₂ sig₇-a me-te {e₂}tur₃-re unu₇ kug nam-diŋir-zu
#lem: gara[cream]; sissig[green-yellow]; mete[appropriate thing]; tur[animal stall]; unu[dwelling]; kug[purify]; namdiŋir[divinity]
#etcsl: line-id=17

